body:
I get error when I declare `inout` port of unpacked structure type. It looks that port variables are emitted as variables of type `char`.
Here is an example:
```systemverilog
typedef struct {
   bit x;
} my_struct_t;

module mh1 (inout my_struct_t a, inout my_struct_t b);
   assign b.x = a.x;
endmodule

module t;
   my_struct_t a, b;
   mh1 u_mh1(a, b);
   initial begin
      a.x = 1;
      #1;
      if (b.x) begin
         $write("*-* All Finished *-*\n");
         $finish;
      end
      else begin
         $stop;
      end
   end
endmodule
```
